med:COVID19 med:hasSymptom med:Fever .
med:COVID19 med:hasSymptom med:Cough .
med:COVID19 med:hasSymptom med:Dyspnea .
med:COVID19 med:hasSymptom med:Fatigue .

# Mental Health
med:Depression med:hasSymptom med:Fatigue .
