med:AnxietyDisorder med:hasSymptom med:Insomnia .
med:AnxietyDisorder med:hasSymptom med:Palpitations .
med:AnxietyDisorder med:hasSymptom med:Nausea .

# ==============================================================================
# DISEASE-TREATMENT ASSERTIONS (treatedBy)
# ==============================================================================
med:Hypertension med:treatedBy med:Antihypertensive .
