# DISEASE-DIAGNOSTIC ASSERTIONS (diagnosedBy)
# ==============================================================================
med:Hypertension med:diagnosedBy med:BloodTest .
med:CoronaryArteryDisease med:diagnosedBy med:ECG .
med:CoronaryArteryDisease med:diagnosedBy med:Echocardiogram .
